title: The Blanks - Riding the Wave [INCOMPLETE]
description:
Ted&#039;s band (from Scrubs) released an album called Riding the Wave, available in its entirety exclusively on CDBaby.com. A truncated version of that album is available for digital download on other music distribution sites, such as Amazon.com.

This torrent includes those songs plus a few songs from the full album that I have found.
